<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4276] AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The master debug logs are quite verbose, so people don&apos;t usually have them all on. But, when trying to debug why a cluster&apos;s in a bad state due to META or ROOT issues, it&apos;s really helpful to have this info. So, for any transition info for these important regions, we should always log details at INFO level.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12520527">HBASE-4276</key>
