                            <comment id="13094122" author="tlipcon" created="Tue, 30 Aug 2011 21:45:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed this, then realized I made the mistake of only checking for isMetaRegion, and didn&apos;t do the same for ROOT. I reverted the commit. Here&apos;s an improved patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
