                            <comment id="13094189" author="hudson" created="Tue, 30 Aug 2011 23:48:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in HBase-TRUNK #2163 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-TRUNK/2163/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-TRUNK/2163/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276&quot; title=&quot;AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4276&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;  AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions.&lt;br/&gt;
Revert previous commit of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276&quot; title=&quot;AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4276&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Realized after committing that the conditions should check&lt;br/&gt;
isMetaTable || isRootRegion, not just isMetaTable. Will recommit&lt;br/&gt;
a fixed version.&lt;br/&gt;
Previous commit purported to revert &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276&quot; title=&quot;AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4276&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but accidentally reverted &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4293&quot; title=&quot;More verbose logging in ServerShutdownHandler for meta/root cases&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4293&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4293&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This commit re-applies &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4293&quot; title=&quot;More verbose logging in ServerShutdownHandler for meta/root cases&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4293&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4293&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. The next commit will &lt;em&gt;actually&lt;/em&gt; revert &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276&quot; title=&quot;AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4276&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Revert previous commit of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276&quot; title=&quot;AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4276&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Realized after committing that the conditions should check&lt;br/&gt;
isMetaTable || isRootRegion, not just isMetaTable. Will recommit&lt;br/&gt;
a fixed version.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4276&quot; title=&quot;AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4276&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;  AssignmentManager debug logs should be at INFO level for META/ROOT regions.&lt;/p&gt;

